    <item>
      <title>伊朗迈出放松社交媒体禁令的第一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/iran-takes-first-steps-toward-easing-its-broad-social-media-bans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，将开始放松一些全球最严格的互联网限制，解除对 WhatsApp 和 Google Play 的禁令 — — 这表明，在伊朗伊斯兰共和国面临重大经济和外交政策挑战之际，当局希望安抚国内反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/iran-takes-first-steps-toward-easing-its-broad-social-media-bans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 16:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗否认利用儿童袭击欧洲以色列目标的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/iran-denies-it-used-children-to-strike-israeli-targets-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗否认瑞典和比利时调查人员的说法，称伊朗伊斯兰共和国招募儿童袭击其境内的以色列目标，并称其“荒谬可笑”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/iran-denies-it-used-children-to-strike-israeli-targets-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 16:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新任总理贝鲁能否在法国危险的政治环境中生存下来？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/new-french-prime-minister-francois-bayrou-can-he-bring-stability-at-last</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月初，法国议会下院 60 多年来首次推翻政府，迫使总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 寻找一位能够驾驭法国严重分裂的政治格局的总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/new-french-prime-minister-francois-bayrou-can-he-bring-stability-at-last</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 14:59:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其计划与叙利亚启动海事协议谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/turkey-plans-to-start-maritime-agreement-negotiations-with-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其交通和基础设施部长阿卜杜勒卡迪尔·乌拉洛格鲁表示，土耳其计划与叙利亚展开谈判，划定地中海海上边界。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/turkey-plans-to-start-maritime-agreement-negotiations-with-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 12:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理寻求削减预算以推翻前任内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/french-premier-pledges-budget-cuts-that-toppled-prior-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国新任总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁誓言要大幅缩减国家赤字至 GDP 的 5% 左右，这一计划有可能重演导致上届政府倒台的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/french-premier-pledges-budget-cuts-that-toppled-prior-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 10:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克当选总统希望在动乱后恢复投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/president-elect-chapo-plans-dialog-to-end-mozambique-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克新任总统丹尼尔·查波计划举行民族和解谈判，以解决不断升级的政治危机，该危机已导致数十人死亡，并导致这个天然气资源丰富的国家经济增长停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/president-elect-chapo-plans-dialog-to-end-mozambique-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 09:09:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>专家组陷入僵局后拜登将就美国钢铁收购案做出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/biden-to-decide-on-us-steel-acquisition-after-panel-deadlocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司拟以 123 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司，这一交易距离受阻又近了一步，因为美国国家安全委员会在审查中陷入僵局，并将最终决定权交给了总统乔·拜登，而拜登曾多次表示反对这笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/biden-to-decide-on-us-steel-acquisition-after-panel-deadlocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 01:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
